body.description: Coconut Pulling Oil (8 Fl.Oz), Mint Oil Pulling Mouthwash with Tongue Scraper, with 100% Pure and natural ingredients to help with bad breath and supports healthy gums and oral for a brighter, healthier smile. Benefits of Pulling Oil: Helps cleaning teeth and oral care. Helps fresher breath. Helps reduce bad breath. Helps whiten, cleanse and protect your teeth, tongue and gums. Natural Formula: Alcohol and Fluoride Free. No Preservatives and No Artificial Flavors. Cruelty Free and Never Tested on Animals. How to Use: Shake well. Place a tablespoon of Pulling Oil in your mouth and swish it vigorously through your teeth for about 3 to 10 minutes while keeping your mouth closed. DO NOT SWALLOW. After you're done, spit out the oil and rinse your mouth with warm water and brush as normal. Use the provided tongue scraper to clean your tongue. Per Ayurvedic philosophy, oil pulling is best performed in the morning on an empty stomach. INGREDIENTS: 100% Pure Coconut Oil, Peppermint Essential oil.
